  <section*|Notes>

  On this website, I've shared some notes from my Ph.D. journey. If you
  encounter any problems or spot any inaccuracies in the notes, please don't
  hesitate to reach out to me. You can email me at <href|yansong@liii.pro>.
  For a complete list of all the notes I've published here, please refer to
  <hlink|here|list-articles.tm>.

  \;
